     &mt RBKT GRAVE  &hml LGUI A     &hml LALT S     &hml LCTRL D    &hml LSHFT F    &kp G               &kp H           &hmr RSHFT J    &hmr RCTRL K    &hmr RALT L     &hmr RGUI SEMI  &kp SQT 
